modName: Skein of Magnus by disenchanting Archmages Robes
summary: Ability to disenchant the Archmage Robes and enchant Skein of Magnus
descriptionHtml:
This allows you to disenchant the Archmage Robes and enchant Skein of Magnus. Unzip to Skyrim/data folder and enable.

IF you already downloaded the previous file (Disenchant Archmage Robes) just delete that mod and install this one. It is 100% fixed.
author: punkmanj
